src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過儘可能唔好停得太近其他車 大陸好多開門撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa365755adaf8805ba2c5db8ec79cab4932fc5c","tid":43032,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問個白痴問題<br />\n巴打你有搞大陸車牌咖何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我驚你無搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比左成千銀搞 不過咁多年都唔敢上去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 大陸停車場個d 點搞</blockquote><br />\n一樣咁搞既姐<br />\n入場取卡出場比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過儘可能唔好停得太近其他車 大陸好多開門撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦 即係同香港差唔多<br />\n有丫姐 收錢？<br />\n<br />\n因為我前排去加拿大自駕<br />\n個到d 停車場 無閘 <br />\n自出自入 但就有部機禁ticket 比錢<br />\nD 機好得意 係入自己國際車牌個no.<br />\n唔係架車個車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15026f87481414335b33d142e4de911a2f7e8d3c","tid":43032,"uid":44287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"眼仔事小，你最要小心「區間測速」。<br />\n區間測速，係個段路你快過某一個時間行完，佢就當你超速，然後就開罰單。"},{"pid":"18b3e38aa75deaeb171255f73f8e304fb7c552ce","tid":43032,"uid":44287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼仔事小，你最要小心「區間測速」。<br />\n區間測速，係個段路你快過某一個時間行完，佢就當你超速，然後就開罰單。</blockquote><br />\n同埋留意深圳上高速係自己㩒掣攞咭，所以要揸近部機小小，唔係會㩒唔到嗰掣。"},{"pid":"1120c0b5222afc57dc57b8ba0a00db6866681c6f","tid":43032,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問個白痴問題<br />\n巴打你有搞大陸車牌咖何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我驚你無搞</blockquote><br />\n有啊, 係鏗錩攪1900蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61adcfffe193ce8906adcb1fa47a4d1bc6edc2d8","tid":43032,"uid":21108,